data.description: This gorgeous home is waiting for you! 4 bedroom, 2.5 baths with a loft/flex space. All bedrooms and the laundry room are upstairs. Downstairs you will notice a designated dining room with trey ceilings connected by a galley pantry to the spacious kitchen. Granite countertops in the kitchen as well as ample storage. As you venture into the back you will step into a screened in Carolina room. Connected to the Carolina room is a deck perfect for entertaining and grilling. Owners are also conveying play set to new owners as gift. Large fenced in backyard and faux wood blinds throughout the interior. As if all this wasn’t great as is, sellers had new roof put on in 2022 and septic has been freshly pumped! Run don’t walk!!
